comment:
* Represents a planned workout that should be completed by the user.
 *
 * @hide
 * @see PlannedExerciseSessionRecord

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setNotes(String notes)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified notes.

methods.name: public String getTitle()
methods.comment: returns the title of this planned workout.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setTitle(String title)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified title.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setHasExplicitTime(boolean hasExplicitTime)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified notes.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setExerciseBlocks(List<PlannedExerciseBlockInternal> blocks)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified {@link PlannedExerciseBlockInternal} entries.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setCompletedExerciseSessionId(UUID id)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified completed exercise session id.

methods.name: public List<PlannedExerciseBlockInternal> getExerciseBlocks()
methods.comment: returns the {@link PlannedExerciseBlockInternal} entries associated with this object.

methods.name: public UUID getCompletedExerciseSessionId()
methods.comment: returns the UUID of the exercise session which completed this plan, if it exists.

methods.name: public boolean getHasExplicitTime()
methods.comment: returns whether this object has an explicit time set.

methods.name: public int getExerciseType()
methods.comment: returns the exercise type of this planned workout.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecordInternal setExerciseType(int exerciseType)
methods.comment: returns this object with the specified exercise type.

methods.name: public PlannedExerciseSessionRecord toExternalRecord()
methods.comment: Convert this object to an external representation.
